aping the city that KOs a Hero from the HQ (that costs 6 or less) can KO a Haunted Hero. Card effects that let you \\u201cgain a Hero from the HQ\\u201d or \\u201cPut a Hero from the HQ on the bottom of the Hero Deck\\u201d still work on Haunted Heroes. However, card effects that say \\u201crecruit a Hero from the HQ for free\\u201d don\'t work on Haunted Heroes, since you can\'t recruit them.<\\/li><li>If something causes a Haunted Hero to leave the HQ, then the Haunting Villain stays in that HQ space and Haunts the new Hero that arrives to refill that HQ space.<\\/li><li>If an HQ space is \\u201cdestroyed,\\u201d KO any Haunted Hero there and the Haunting Villain there enters the city, ignoring any Ambush effects.<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}',0),
